OL,3,CWoman with terminal cancer calls for
OL,4,Cimproved palliative care in NI
OL,6,FA major inquiry by Stormont's Health
OL,7,FCommittee has found that palliative
OL,8,Fcare services are failing terminally-
OL,9,Fill patients and their families, with
OL,10,Fthe challenge of accessing support
OL,11,Fcausing long-term trauma.
OL,13,FThe year-long investigation found that
OL,14,Fterminally-ill patients were dying on
OL,15,FEmergency Department corridors because
OL,16,Fof a lack of out-of-hours palliative
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
