OL,6,FThe inquiry report, published on
OL,7,FTuesday, also found that there is a
OL,8,Fpostcode lottery for patients and
OL,9,Ftheir families when trying to access
OL,10,Fpalliative and end-of-life care.
OL,12,FThe report has made several urgent
OL,13,Frecommendations to improve services.
