OL,3,CWoman with terminal cancer calls for
OL,4,Cimproved palliative care in NI
OL,6,FMLA Philip McGuigan, who is Chair of
OL,7,Fthe Health Committee, said: "We are
OL,8,Fbehind the curve here in the north
OL,9,Fwith regard to care across these
OL,10,Fislands, both in terms of funding and
OL,11,Falso more importantly in terms of
OL,12,Faccess that people can get."
OL,14,FMeanwhile MLA Danny Donnelly, who is
OL,15,Fthe committee's Deputy Chair, said:
OL,16,F"People are having different
OL,17,Fexperiences, not all of them good.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
