OL,3,CWoman with terminal cancer calls for
OL,4,Cimproved palliative care in NI
OL,6,F"We've heard some quite upsetting
OL,7,Fcases that people are inappropriately
OL,8,Fbeing taken to A&E when they're in
OL,9,Ftheir last days.
OL,11,F"We need to be doing more in community
OL,12,Fand building that capacity in
OL,13,Fcommunity so that people can die with
OL,14,Fdignity."
OL,16,FThe report also flagged that the
OL,17,Fcurrent funding model for hospices is
OL,18,Fnot fit for the future.
