OL,3,CWoman with terminal cancer calls for
OL,4,Cimproved palliative care in NI
OL,6,FOn this, Trevor McCartney from NI
OL,7,FHospice, said: "Northern Ireland has
OL,8,Fbeen shown to have the greatest need
OL,9,Ffor palliative care, in particular
OL,10,Fspecialist palliative care in all of
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,F"That being the case, with only four
OL,14,Fhospices that are constrained with the
OL,15,Fresources they have at the minute, it
OL,16,Fis a challenge and will continue to be
OL,17,Fa challenge unless we are funded
OL,18,Fappropriately to ensure that we can
OL,19,Fdevelop and expand our services to
OL,20,Fmeet that growing need."
