OL,3,CWoman with terminal cancer calls for
OL,4,Cimproved palliative care in NI
OL,6,FFor Christine Campbell, who is living
OL,7,Fwith terminal cancer, palliative care
OL,8,Fis about making every day count in the
OL,9,Fface of a future she can no longer
OL,10,Fcontrol.
OL,12,FShe said: "Palliative care is a really
OL,13,Fscary thing to hear, and when I heard
OL,14,Fit, I felt like my world had stopped
OL,15,Fturning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
