OL,3,CWoman with terminal cancer calls for
OL,4,Cimproved palliative care in NI
OL,6,F"It is there to support people who
OL,7,Fhave a terminal diagnosis, whether
OL,8,Fit's cancer, like myself, or it's
OL,9,Fheart failure, renal failure, lung
OL,10,Fconditions, anybody with a life
OL,11,Flimiting condition.
OL,13,FShe is campaigning so others get the
OL,14,Fsame help that she has had, so they
OL,15,Fcan cherish the moments the matter.
OL,17,FShe said: "The life that I thought I
OL,18,Fwas going to have has been shortened
OL,19,Fand that sort of control has been
OL,20,Ftaken away from me in a way.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
